#: mate-system-monitor.appdata.xml.in:7 mate-system-monitor.desktop.in.in:3
msgid "MATE System Monitor"
msgstr "MATE-Systeem-Överwacher"

#: mate-system-monitor.appdata.xml.in:8
msgid "A Process and resource monitor for MATE Desktop"
msgstr "Een Överwacher över Prozessen un Ressourcen för de MATE Schrievdisk"

#: mate-system-monitor.appdata.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"MATE System Monitor allows to graphically view and manipulate the running "
"processes on your system. It also provides an overview of available "
"resources, such as CPU and memory."
msgstr ""
"MATE-Systeem-Överwacher verlöövt, de Prozessen, wat up dienem Systeem lopen,"
" graphisk to wiesen un to stüren. ’t gifft ok eene Översicht över "
"verföögbaare Ressourcen as CPU un Spieker."

#: mate-system-monitor.appdata.xml.in:15
msgid ""
"MATE System Monitor is a fork of GNOME System Monitor and part of the MATE "
"Desktop Environment. If you would like to know more about MATE and System "
"Monitor, please visit the project's home page."
msgstr ""
"MATE-Systeem-Överwacher is eene Gavel vun GNOME-Systeem-Överwacher un Deel "
"vun de MATE-Schrievdisk-Umgeven. Wenn du mehr över MATE un Systeem-"
"Överwacher utfinnen willst, besöök bidde de Internettsied vum Projekt."

