#. xgettext: secondary alert message
#: src/procdialogs.cpp:104
msgid ""
"Killing a process may destroy data, break the session or introduce a "
"security risk. Only unresponsive processes should be killed."
msgstr ""
"Eenen Prozess doodtomaken, kann Daten ramponeren, de Törn kaputt maken of "
"eene Sekerheids-Gefahr infögen. Blots Prozessen, wat nich antern, sallen "
"doodmaakt worden."

#. xgettext: secondary alert message
#: src/procdialogs.cpp:110
msgid ""
"Ending a process may destroy data, break the session or introduce a security"
" risk. Only unresponsive processes should be ended."
msgstr ""
"Eenen Prozess to ennen, kann Daten ramponeren, de Törn kaputt maken of eene "
"Sekerheids-Gefahr infögen. Blots Prozessen, wat nich antern, sallen ennt "
"worden."

